getAssetPrice.t.sol
├─ when the asset streams price is not stale
│  └─ it should return the streams price and timestamp
└─ when the asset streams price is stale
   ├─ when the data feed decimals is lower than 18
   │  └─ it should scale the price up to 18 decimals
   ├─ when the data feed decimals is greater than 18
   │  └─ it should scale the price down to 18 decimals
   └─ it should the scaled data feed price and timestamp
